snippet.title: Creatures of the Deep - Official Gameplay Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the underwater world in this new fishing adventure game for your phone. 🏝️🐟🦑

DISCOVER the World's Most Exotic Locations
CATCH unique fish, creatures and monsters
SOLVE  the local mystery

You never know what's at the end of your hook!

DOWNLOAD NOW!
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/creatures-of-the-deep/id1556204048
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=pl.idreams.cotd


Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/ymQRUGQg
Follow on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/creatures.of.the.deep.game/
Like Us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CreaturesOfTheDeep.Game
Official website: https://cotd.idreams.pl
